---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Learn more about me and how to get in touch.">
  <article class="about-page">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1 class="page-title">About</h1>
      <p class="page-subtitle">Learn more about me and how to get in touch.</p>
    </header>

    <section class="bio">
      <p>
        I'm Mohit — a builder focused on AI-powered products and workflow automation.
        I help teams ship faster by building custom tools, prototypes, and systems that
        leverage the latest in AI and automation.
      </p>
      <p>
        My background spans product development, software engineering, and AI applications.
        I enjoy taking complex problems and turning them into simple, effective solutions.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="services">
      <h2>What I help with</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>AI product development</strong> — Building products that use LLMs, computer vision, or other AI capabilities</li>
        <li><strong>Workflow automation</strong> — Streamlining processes with custom integrations and tools</li>
        <li><strong>Rapid prototyping</strong> — Quickly validating ideas with working prototypes</li>
        <li><strong>Technical consulting</strong> — Advising on architecture, tooling, and AI strategy</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="work-with-me">
      <h2>Work with me</h2>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <span class="availability">Available for projects</span>
      </div>
      <p>
        If you're working on something interesting and think I could help, I'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <ul class="contact-links">
        <li>
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:your@email.com">your@email.com</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Twitter/X:</strong> <a href="https://twitter.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener">@yourhandle</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Schedule a call:</strong> <a href="https://calendly.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Calendly</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .page-header {
    margin-bottom: clamp(1.2rem, 2.4vw, 1.8rem);
  }

  .page-title {
    margin: 0 0 0.25rem 0;
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 1.8rem);
    font-family: var(--entry-title-font);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .page-subtitle {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    letter-spacing: 0.012em;
  }

  .bio {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .bio p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .services {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .services h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .services ul {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .services li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .work-with-me {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .work-with-me h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .cta-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .availability {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .availability::before {
    content: '';
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    background: #22c55e;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .contact-links {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .contact-links li {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .contact-links strong {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 120px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: normal;
  }
</style>
